'''亞當·派翠克·迪凡'''（{{lang-en|'''Adam Patrick DeVine'''}}，{{bd|1983年|11月7日}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.twitter.com/ADAMDEVINE/status/398611948704522241|title=Tweet from DeVine's verified account regarding his birthday|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|first=Adam|last=DeVine|date=2013-11-07|accessdate=2014-05-12|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009175352/https://twitter.com/ADAMDEVINE/status/398611948704522241|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Omaha">{{cite news|url=http://www.omaha.com/article/20130809/GO/308099869|title=Adam DeVine, Omaha native, scores recurring role in 'Modern Family'|work=[[Omaha_World-Herald|Omaha World-Herald]]|first=Bob|last=Fishbach|date=2013-08-09|accessdate=2015-05-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131016111731/http://www.omaha.com/article/20130809/GO/308099869|archivedate=2013-10-16}}</ref>是一位美國男演員、喜劇演員、製片人和編劇。較著名的是在電視劇《[[初入職場|初入職場]]》（2011年至今）<ref name="Omaha"/>和《{{link-en|亞當迪凡的歡樂派對|Adam DeVine's House Party}}》（2013年至今）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/q-a-the-workaholic-life-of-adam-devine-20140304|title=Q&A: The 'Workaholic' Life of Adam DeVine|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|first=Charles|last=Thorp|date=2014-03-04|accessdate=2015-05-15|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143743/https://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/q-a-the-workaholic-life-of-adam-devine-20140304|dead-url=no}}</ref>中的演出和擔任共同創作者。而他也在歌舞電影《[[歌喉讚|歌喉讚]]》（2012年）和《[[歌喉讚2|歌喉讚2]]》（2015年）中飾演邦普·艾倫<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/interviews/a35031/adam-devine-pitch-perfect-2-interview/|title=Adam Devine on Singing in Public, Gangster-Rapping Wizards, and Romantic Gestures|work=[[Esquire_(magazine)|Esquire]]|first=Emily|last=Zemler|accessdate=2015-05-15|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917143758/https://www.esquire.com/entertainment/movies/interviews/a35031/adam-devine-pitch-perfect-2-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==早期生活==
亞當·迪凡出生於[[愛荷華州|愛荷華州]]的[[滑鐵盧_(愛荷華州)|滑鐵盧]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wcfcourier.com/entertainment/waterloo-native-becomes-a-workaholic/article_6a50362c-45ec-11e1-8f4f-0019bb2963f4.html|title=Waterloo Native Becomes a 'Workaholic'|first=Amie|last=Steffen|date=2012-01-23|work=Waterloo Cedar Falls Courier|accessdate=2015-09-05|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629065017/http://wcfcourier.com/entertainment/waterloo-native-becomes-a-workaholic/article_6a50362c-45ec-11e1-8f4f-0019bb2963f4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父母為丹尼斯（Dennis）和彭妮·迪凡（Penny DeVine）<ref name="Omaha"/>。2002年，他畢業於[[內布拉斯加州|內布拉斯加州]][[奧馬哈_(內布拉斯加州)|奧馬哈]]的{{link-en|米勒德南高中|Millard South High School}}<ref name="Omaha"/>。1995年6月，在他11歲時，被42噸重的混凝土卡車撞傷；讓當時在對街騎自行車的他造成雙腿多處骨折，需要進行超過三年的多次手術，並花了兩年再度學走<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/adam-devine/bio/324819 |title=Adam DeVine Biography |work=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130115183122/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/adam-devine/bio/324819 |archivedate=2013年1月15日 |accessdate=2016年4月28日 }}</ref>。

迪凡和朋友{{link-en|布雷克·安德森|Blake Anderson}}一起就讀了{{link-en|橘郡海岸學院|Orange Coast College}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?NR=1&feature=fvwp&v=gt9VaUl_G8E|title=Adam DeVine on YouTube|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|accessdate=2013-12-31|archive-date=2014-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140129171431/http://www.youtube.com/watch?NR=1&feature=fvwp&v=gt9VaUl_G8E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，他搬到了[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，在那裡開始從事演員和喜劇演員的工作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nationallampoon.com/lemmings/bio_adam.html|title=National Lampoon Lemmings Comedy Troupe!|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111220040931/http://www.nationallampoon.com/lemmings/bio_adam.html|archivedate=2011-12-20|publisher=National Lampoon|accessdate=2012-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="moc">{{cite web|url=http://www.mailordercomedy.com/bios.html|title=Bios|publisher=Mail Order Comedy|date=2011-04-06|accessdate=2012-07-22|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523075015/http://www.mailordercomedy.com/bios.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

